    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html\"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/administrative-gender</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFgenderIdentity.html\">VF_genderIdentity</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-unknown\">unknown</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Unknown</td><td>Unknown.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-female\">female</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Female</td><td>Female.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-male\">male</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Male</td><td>Male.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Other</td><td>Other.</td><td/></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedElements/2-.024</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFgenderIdentity.html\">VF_genderIdentity</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>N</td><td>DOES NOT WISH TO DISCLOSE</td><td><span title=\"SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET\">&lt;</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-unknown\">unknown</a></td></tr><tr><td>F</td><td>FEMALE</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-female\">female</a></td></tr><tr><td>M</